parameters.name: 【純愛系】わたしたちはひとり

parameters: "...Ah, right. I got hit trying to protect Makoto."

"That's right. You were unlucky to get hit right on the chin
and you passed out."

"Of all places, the chin... Wait? What about the opening
ceremony?"

"It's over. It's already... evening now. You overslept in
the morning, and now a nap after lunch? You really do sleep
a lot, Mamoru."

"I slept that much...? It's a shame, it was a day I could
have gone home early, feels like I wasted it."

"Hey Mamoru. Why did you protect me back then? You know,
don't you? That I'm a martial artist with a black belt."

"I wouldn't have lost to a guy like that, and as you saw,
none of the other students tried to help me."
"And yet, why is it always you...?"

"Why...? Well, if a girl is being attacked, isn't it normal
to help her?"

"...I see, a girl, huh. Mamoru, you always treat me as a
girl."

"No, not at all. In fact, I'm quite happy. You're the only
one who has never treated me like a prince..."

"Ah, sorry. Forget what I just said. It's getting late,
shall we go home together after a long time?"

"Makoto is my precious childhood friend. That's why I'll
always protect you, no matter what."

"Hehe, what are you saying all of a sudden? I'm everyone's
prince. There's no need for me to be protected..."

"Makoto is not a prince! Makoto is just a girl! That's why
I... I..."

(Crap. What am I doing? I got carried away talking and
blurted out something outrageous.)

(No, but wait? Isn't this a chance to confess? I was
planning to tell her someday, so maybe I should just go for
it...)
告白する（エンディング）
"I-I... I've liked you since a long time ago!!"

"Of course, I know I'm not good enough for you. But still, I
like you!"

(No, was it a mistake...? Of course, it is... How could
Makoto ever like someone like me...)
"I love you too, Mamoru! Will you go out with me?"

"Is it okay!? Really!? You're really okay with someone like
me!?"

"What... You were the one who said you liked me first,
weren't you?"

"No, no no no no. Sure, that's true, but I didn't expect you
to actually ask me out..."

"Ah, that's true! It's like I'm the one who confessed! No,
let's do it over! Do it over! Mamoru, say it again!"

"Eh, eh...? Uh, well then... *cough* Makoto...! Will you go
out with me?"

"Yes, I'd be delighted to accept!! I'm so happy... Mamoru, I
love you!!"

"Ugh!! My chest, the impact is... Ma-Makoto... let go for a
second...!"

"No way!! I will never let go!! Mamoru!! I love you!! I love
you so muchhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh!!"

And so, I happily ended up together with Makoto. Honestly, I
never imagined my confession would work out, but who would
have thought that Makoto and I would both feel the same way.

From what I heard, it seems that Makoto was fed up with
being treated like a prince and has always liked me because
I treated her like a girl and protected her in various ways.

Makoto was everyone's prince, but in reality, maybe she was
waiting for a prince of her own. Well, I'm certainly not cut
out to be a prince...
恥ずかしいから誤魔化す

"Uh... um... I... I think of Makoto as a very important
friend!!"

"Th-th-th-that's right!! Makoto and I have been great
friends since we were kids!! Please continue to get along
with me!!"

"Awawa, I've really made her angry... Maybe things would
have gone well if I had confessed?"

"No, that can't be right. Makoto and I are just too
mismatched..."

"I'll have to send a message later to apologize. For now, I
guess I'll head home..."
